<article class="row hentry post-265223 to4_article_post type-to4_article_post status-publish has-post-thumbnail category-op-ed tag-chile tag-ecuador tag-global-solidarity tag-haiti tag-iraq tag-lebanon tag-neoliberalism tag-protests section-economy-and-labor primary_topic-labor" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/OpinionNewsArticle">
